{
  "texts": [
    "Subsequently, it can leverage its machine learning algorithms to identify patterns in the image and give a conclusion (7).",
    "GPT has the potential to be a valuable resource in pathology education and collaborate with pathologists during diagnosis (8, 9).",
    "The performances of GPT-4 show a similar level of the pathologist, even outperforming a trained pathologist in online questionand-answer exchanges (10).",
    "Compared to Google Bard, a LLM produced by Google, GPT-4 outperformed in terms of accuracy when it came to grading non-alcoholic fatty liver disease based on histology images (11).",
    "Compared to pathology residents, the diagnostic performance of GPT-4 is consistent but slightly inferior based on pathology image (12)."
  ]
}